dc_description_s: This data represents zoning for Outagamie County, Wisconsin in 2024 and includes the layers 'OUTAGAMIE_AIRPORT_2024,' 'OUTAGAMIE_GENERAL_2024,' and 'OUTAGAMIE_SHORELAND_2024.' [Airport: This feature class was derived off of the 1990 Zoning Ordinance Z-16-90. This ordinance covers airport property, the airport industrial park and the airport overylay districts. Zone 3A was created in March of 2012.General: This is a polygon geodatabase depicting the local zoning of parcels under Outagamie County Zoning jurisdiction. Outagamie County created new zoning maps for the areas of the County that have exclusive agriculture zoning that are under County jurisdiction. The County also updated the text of the County Zoning Ordinance to meet requirements enforced by DATCP to meet requirements of chapter 91 of the Wisconsin State Statutes dealing with farmland preservation starting in 2013. ]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://data-ocgis.opendata.arcgis.com/
